Metrorail has adjusted its timetable for the festive season. CAPE TOWN - Metrorail is adjusting its train timetable for the holiday season that will commence on Monday (12 December).And there s good news for beach lovers, as there''ll be additional trains on the coastal route.Metrorail spokesperson Riana Scott chats about the festive season timetable and commuter safety in the SoundCloud interview above.